posting_body: ['REF# 10R180', '$3000 · 1/1 · Unfurnished · The Axis On Brickell Cond · 693 Sqft · Brickell', 'Call ➟ Text ➟ WhatsApp', "📲 786'*'5O5'*'4314", 'Carlos Manchego', 'Goldstein Realty', 'show contact info', 'Spacious 1 bed / 1 bath condo located in the heart of Brickell.', 'Complete with white porcelain floor (no carpet), top of the line appliances, and a beautiful balcony.', 'The bathroom features a separate tub and tastefully renovated shower.', 'Large bedroom with balcony access and walk-in closet.', 'The building, AXIS, is well known for its wonderful amenities: two pools, jacuzzi, state of the art gym, WIFI service in common areas, game room, play ground, kids room, conference room, party room, pool tables, valet parking available, a must see!', 'Axis association requires $500 deposit for common areas.', 'Read Less', 'REF# 10R180', 'tags:', 'uptown lofts, parc lofts, 1060 brickell, star lofts on the bay, villaggio in the grove, lofts in the grove, the sail condo, baltus house, neo loft, brickell on the river, skyline on brickell, 1060 brickell, latitude on the river, 23 biscayne bay, courvoisier courts, star lofts, the loft ii, the loft 1 downtown, wind by neo, platinum condos, brickell flatiron, brickell city centre, aria on the bay, grovenor house, ten museum park, axis on brickell, paramount miami worldcenter, brickellhouse, south 27 lofts, brickell bay club, bay park towers, infinity,, 1010 brickell, brand new', '_mr10']
